divs: Sighting Detailslooking south off of my back deck noticed 2 large white orbs following the same path. the size of Jupiter with a span of the size of a cigarette pack at arms length apart. traveling out of the south with a path to the N.E. they were visible for about 1 minute. the first one faded out first and the second went through its path and seemed to turn east before it also faded. no blinking lights and no sound. have seen many "satellites" and some "others". have never seen a double b4. moved here from sheboygan in Dec. 0-8 and am pleased to see so many unexplainable things.
